	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I got an extra Olympus no tatakai for cheap yesterday (my original one was not working properly sometime). I was hoping to be able to use the old one as a test dev board since the english one was using an MMC1. After searching on the net, they used an UNROM instead... So it seems some game when they were ported were changed mappers in the US. I'm learning new things everyday, yay! (...)  Oh well. I don't mind to have a spare cart for the price I paid anyway.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


